videos.description: Aislinn Konig sends a nice bounce pass to Kayla Jones who cuts to the hoop for an early layup vs. Louisville.

videos.headline: NC State's Jones scores off the inbounds

videos.description: Dana Evans shows off her speed as she rushes into the paint, fakes out her NC State defender and hits an and-1 in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Evans fakes and draws a foul for Louisville and-1) 2020/2/13

videos.headline: Evans fakes and draws a foul for Louisville and-1

videos.description: Jazmine Jones picks off NC State and takes the ball the other way for a slick Louisville bucket.

videos.description: Aislinn Konig shows off her sweet footwork inside the paint as she fights to get around her Louisville defender on her way to the rim for two.

videos.headline: NC State's Konig uses fancy footwork for two

videos.description: Kylee Shook pokes the ball loose and away from NC State, setting up Jazmine Jones with a nifty Louisville layup on the other end.

videos.description: Jada Boyd gets the NC State crowd on their feet with two consecutive shots, the first a nifty spin move on her defender for two and second, a tough and-1 jumper.
